    低波動因子¶

    以股價高低區間計算波動率，找出低波動、創新高的股票。

    In [ ]:
    Copied! 
    from finlab import data
from finlab.backtest import sim

close = data.get('us_price:close')
high = data.get('us_price:high')
low = data.get('us_price:low')
vol =  data.get('us_price:volume')
marketcap = data.get('us_daily_metrics:marketcap')


# 收盤價近5日至少有1日創收盤價近100日創新
condition1 = (close == close.rolling(100).max()).sustain(5,1)
# 近60日股價高低區間在25%內
condition2 = (1 - low.rolling(60).min()/high.rolling(60).max()) < 0.25
# 收盤價低於整體市場分級的50%
condition3 = close <= close.quantile_row(0.5)
# 成交均量不能太低
condition4 = vol.average(10) > 10000

position = condition1 & condition2 & condition3 & condition4
position *= vol
position = position[position > 0].is_smallest(10)

report = sim(position, resample="2w", fee_ratio=0, tax_ratio=0, position_limit=0.1, stop_loss=0.05, name="美股低價股低波動策略")
# report.display()
    from finlab import data from finlab.backtest import sim close = data.get('us_price:close') high = data.get('us_price:high') low = data.get('us_price:low') vol = data.get('us_price:volume') marketcap = data.get('us_daily_metrics:marketcap') # 收盤價近5日至少有1日創收盤價近100日創新 condition1 = (close == close.rolling(100).max()).sustain(5,1) # 近60日股價高低區間在25%內 condition2 = (1 - low.rolling(60).min()/high.rolling(60).max()) < 0.25 # 收盤價低於整體市場分級的50% condition3 = close <= close.quantile_row(0.5) # 成交均量不能太低 condition4 = vol.average(10) > 10000 position = condition1 & condition2 & condition3 & condition4 position *= vol position = position[position > 0].is_smallest(10) report = sim(position, resample="2w", fee_ratio=0, tax_ratio=0, position_limit=0.1, stop_loss=0.05, name="美股低價股低波動策略") # report.display()
